00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,740
 nisam znao 29. godine.

506
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:15,080
 Ja krećem da pišem

507
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:16,900
 i mene to ispunjava.

508
00:26:16,900 --> 00:26:19,040
 Sad ja radim posao koji ne volim,

509
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:21,540
