00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:28,220
 Brate, ja sam njoj u 5 minuta dao cijel plan.

551
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,840
 Reku, idemo u one zemlje

552
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:31,340
