1244
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:03,140
 Jer sad,

1245
00:43:03,140 --> 00:43:06,040
 zadnji deset puta nisi preduzio akciju

1246
00:43:06,040 --> 00:43:07,040
 na bilo koju ideju,

1247
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:08,240
