1369
00:45:58,400 --> 00:46:00,800
 Ovo sada pričaš,

1370
00:46:00,800 --> 00:46:02,100
 fantastičan,

1371
00:46:02,720 --> 00:46:05,020
 riječnik,

1372
00:46:05,020 --> 00:46:06,000
